02:17.417 --> 02:18.884
Your girlfriend is on hold.

02:18.952 --> 02:21.216
-Hold on a second.
-How could you put me on hold?

02:21.288 --> 02:24.086
-What was it, Mr. Hawkins?
-The bus.

02:24.157 --> 02:26.853
I read that they're going to shut down
our bus line.

02:26.927 --> 02:29.259
If they do that, l can't get to work!

02:29.329 --> 02:32.127
Unless they give me a job
in that new mall they're building.

02:32.199 --> 02:34.929
Don't worry. I've been talking
to the people downtown...

02:35.001 --> 02:36.525
and l promise you this:

02:36.603 --> 02:40.266
If they shut down this bus line,
l will drive you to work myself.

02:40.640 --> 02:42.232
