02:53.620 --> 02:58.580
Hi, that's me, Mays Gilliam, aIderman
of the 9th Ward of Washington, D.C.

02:58.892 --> 03:01.224
Not the part of D.C. you're familiar with.

03:01.294 --> 03:05.492
I work in a neighborhood so bad,
you can get shot while you're getting shot.

03:05.765 --> 03:10.099
Around here when people have a problem,
they don't caIl the mayor, they caIl me.

03:16.109 --> 03:17.269
Miss Pearl!

03:18.945 --> 03:20.537
What's going on?

03:23.083 --> 03:26.075
