03:26.152 --> 03:30.088
I don't know what she's talking about.
We checked the house, nobody is in there.

03:30.156 --> 03:32.249
Hey, man, Dionne is her cat.

03:32.325 --> 03:34.987
Whatever. Cats got nine lives. She'll be fine.

03:35.061 --> 03:37.894
Can we let one guy go in
and help this lady get her cat?

03:37.964 --> 03:41.297
Can't do it. Once they laid the explosives,
there's nothing l can do.

03:41.368 --> 03:42.426
She just showed up.

03:42.502 --> 03:45.630
You took the lady's house.
Can you at least let her get her cat?

03:45.705 --> 03:47.764
We didn't take it, we gave her $40,000.

03:47.841 --> 03:51.641
What kind of house is she supposed to get
with $40,000? A crack house?

03:51.711 --> 03:53.941
I think she'd be happy to get out
of this rattrap.

03:54.014 --> 03:56.539
Who are you to call this place a rattrap?

03:56.616 --> 04:00.882
This is my neighborhood, where l'm from.
I got my first bike stolen right there.

04:00.954 --> 04:03.115
My daddy got his bike stolen right there.

04:03.189 --> 04:07.285
When l have a son, l hope he's fortunate
enough to get stuck up right there.

04:07.360 --> 04:10.056
-Can't you let somebody go check?
-We already looked.

04:10.130 --> 04:12.360
There's nothing in there. We got work to do.

04:12.432 --> 04:14.161
Leave the people alone, damn it!

04:14.234 --> 04:15.997
-Let's get this thing going.
-Come on.

04:16.069 --> 04:18.867
-Stop being in such a hurry.
-We've been here all morning.

04:18.939 --> 04:20.839
Let the lady go inside.

04:21.408 --> 04:23.808
Come on, baby! Sugar baby.

04:24.611 --> 04:27.409
Could you at least turn it off?
Let the lady get her cat.

04:27.480 --> 04:30.881
Dionne, baby? l got something for you!

04:32.986 --> 04:34.283
Miss Pearl, no!

04:36.890 --> 04:40.087
All right, turn it off.
Wait till this woman gets her cat.

04:40.193 --> 04:41.683
Shit, it's not working!

04:41.761 --> 04:42.921
Turn it off!

04:43.430 --> 04:45.796
She better get out, it's going to blow!

04:46.099 --> 04:48.533
Miss Pearl! Come out!

04:49.736 --> 04:50.725
No, Mays!

04:52.405 --> 04:54.134
You've only got a minute!

04:57.010 --> 04:59.103
-Fix it! Get to work.
-I'm trying.

04:59.512 --> 05:01.002
Get a union man on this.

05:01.548 --> 05:03.140
Get your ass out!

05:06.119 --> 05:10.180
Miss Pearl, we got to get out of here.
They're going to blow this place up.

05:10.824 --> 05:14.260
They wouldn't do that, baby!
They know we're in here.

05:14.794 --> 05:18.525
I love you, l've known you a long time.
You've seen a lot in your life.

05:18.598 --> 05:21.590
You've seen churches burnt to the ground,
dogs sicced on kids...

05:21.668 --> 05:23.898
you've seen Malcolm X and JFK killed.

05:23.970 --> 05:26.029
They shut up Muhammad Ali
and Richard Pryor.

05:26.106 --> 05:28.802
They gave Magic Johnson AIDS,
turned Michael Jackson white.

05:28.875 --> 05:32.174
Do you really think these people
give a damn about you?

05:54.009 --> 05:57.035
We interrupt the Jay-Z song
to bring you this speciaI bulletin.

05:57.112 --> 05:59.205
PresidentiaI candidate Senator Gaines...

