14:35.397 --> 14:37.388
Man, l want to know

14:37.699 --> 14:41.499
He feels bad, mighty low
Got nowhere to go

14:41.836 --> 14:44.964
What can you do when you're feeling low

14:45.340 --> 14:47.774
