15:16.769 --> 15:18.202
Here we are.

15:18.371 --> 15:20.566
Mays Gilliam, Debra Lassiter.

15:22.208 --> 15:24.438
Nice to meet you. Take a seat.

15:30.182 --> 15:33.276
We know what happened today.
We know you lost your job.

15:34.654 --> 15:36.645
How do you know that? lt just happened.

15:36.722 --> 15:39.122
We're the government. We know everything.

15:39.926 --> 15:42.156
We'd like you to do something for us.

15:42.228 --> 15:45.755
Sure, l'd love to work
on a presidential campaign.

15:46.198 --> 15:48.894
I'll make phone calls, send out fliers.

15:49.602 --> 15:52.093
Who have you guys chosen
to run against Lewis?

15:52.171 --> 15:55.038
That's exactly what we wanted
to talk to you about.

15:55.241 --> 15:58.506
We'd like you to run for President.

16:05.251 --> 16:08.118
-Of what?
-The United States.

16:09.088 --> 16:11.113
-Of what?
-Of America

16:11.524 --> 16:12.513
Which America?

16:12.592 --> 16:13.820
North...

16:14.260 --> 16:15.921
America, Mays.

16:16.128 --> 16:17.720
Get out of here!

16:18.097 --> 16:19.655
We're not joking.

16:20.499 --> 16:23.491
We want you to be the nominee
for the office of President...

16:23.569 --> 16:25.901
of the United States of America

16:31.277 --> 16:33.108
Let me get this straight.

16:33.179 --> 16:37.081
You guys couldn't find anybody else to run?
You couldn't find nobody?

16:37.283 --> 16:38.773
Something is wrong here.

16:38.851 --> 16:40.944
You couldn't find a congressman...

16:41.020 --> 16:43.648
a senator? l'm just an alderman.

16:43.756 --> 16:47.556
Congressmen, senators,
they work with other politicians.

16:47.994 --> 16:50.622
You're an alderman.
You work with the people.

16:50.696 --> 16:54.097
And that's what we want,
a man of the people.

16:54.200 --> 16:55.861
This is a big joke, right?

16:55.935 --> 16:58.028
They've got a hidden camera somewhere.

16:58.104 --> 17:01.437
You all will get a big laugh out of this.
You know what? l don't care.

17:01.507 --> 17:04.964
One of you all will drive me home
because my bike is messed up.

17:05.578 --> 17:07.102
You an American?

17:09.548 --> 17:12.073
-Are you an American?
-Yes.

17:13.653 --> 17:16.348
This isn't just an election. It's a moment.

17:16.555 --> 17:20.012
This is the moment when you have
the opportunity to show boys and girls...

17:20.092 --> 17:22.424
men and women, what America is about.

17:23.429 --> 17:24.896
Look at that.

17:26.232 --> 17:31.101
When l see that, l think of our forefathers
fighting to make this country what it is.

17:31.771 --> 17:36.435
When l see it l think about the guy who has
to scrub Lincoln's balls for minimum wage.

17:37.076 --> 17:40.637
That's why we want you.
You care about the little people.

17:41.514 --> 17:42.879
What will it be?

17:59.065 --> 18:00.794
It gives me great honor...

18:01.033 --> 18:03.331
to accept the party's nomination...

18:03.436 --> 18:04.869
for President...

18:04.937 --> 18:07.804
of the United States ofAmerica.

18:08.641 --> 18:09.630
No!

18:16.457 --> 18:19.085
Welcome to your campaign headquarters.

18:19.593 --> 18:23.120
These folks will do everything they can
to help you get elected.

18:23.297 --> 18:24.958
These are your people.

18:26.066 --> 18:28.034
Here. Let's take a look at this.

18:28.102 --> 18:30.798
Mark, is that cued up? Roll it, please.

18:38.512 --> 18:40.605
This is a great spot.

18:41.715 --> 18:46.015
Ifyou love America,
vote Mays Gilliam for President.

18:51.058 --> 18:52.423
But l'm not in it.

18:53.394 --> 18:54.759
You don't even see my face.

18:54.828 --> 18:57.058
It's a template.
We'll get you in there eventually.

18:57.131 --> 18:59.622
There's a couple of people
l want you to meet.

18:59.700 --> 19:02.669
This is your security director, Mr. Earl.

19:02.770 --> 19:05.432
-You'll be in good hands.
-Pleased to meet you, sir.

19:05.506 --> 19:09.772
If you're in trouble, yell "Security!"
and my people will handle the situation.

19:09.944 --> 19:13.345
This is your decoy, Mays Junior.
He enters events before you.

19:13.414 --> 19:16.247
If anything'll happen to you,
it'll happen to him first.

19:16.317 --> 19:18.478
Tupac could have used a guy like you.

19:18.552 --> 19:22.989
This is Nicollette White, she's
your executive director of lnternal Liaisons.

19:23.057 --> 19:25.423
Call me Nikki.
It will be a pleasure to serve you.

19:25.492 --> 19:28.620
I'm available to you around the clock,
just let me know.

19:29.897 --> 19:33.128
-What does she do?
-She sleeps with you.

19:33.634 --> 19:36.034
We got tired of getting caught up
in sex scandals...

19:36.103 --> 19:38.765
